    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting with my car and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, looks great inside and out, and is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance so you can just hop in and go. I'd love to see it go to a good home\u2014come take it for a spin!",
