      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a deep, glassy finish, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is supple with minimal wear on the bolsters, and all electronic features\u2014from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car has been treated with professional care, boasting a consistent service record that translates to a smooth, quiet ride and responsive handling. It sits on high-tread premium tires and is ready for its next owner to drive away with complete confidence.",
