      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example remains in strong driver-grade condition, benefitting from a recent VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis fatigue. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox shifts with precision, and the factory limited-slip differential ensures linear power delivery through the corners. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain and suspension kinematics are tight, featuring refreshed bushings and a responsive steering rack. A turn-key performance icon for the purist.",
